Subject: RE: [T2] Pulling engine - what work to batch with it?

Trans:
Rebush clutch actuating fork
Reaplce clutch return spring
Replace To bearing
Safety wire new TO clips
Replace tran input shaft seal
Check boots on CVs or swing axel boots
Change trans oil
Grease threads on clutch cable, inspect bowden tubes
Check clutch disk thickness, replace if marginal or suspect or plain old.


Engine
Check endplay
Retorque heads to spec Primarily on t1s, my t4 experience is more limited.
Check main seals as well
Check exhuast system
Engine to body seal for condition.
Tin and thermostat tight and working

AL

...

